headline: HOLDCO ASSET MANAGEMENT RELEASES PRESENTATION TO THE INDEPENDENT DIRECTORS OF KEYCORP
summary: Today, HoldCo Asset Management, LP ("HoldCo"), a Florida-based investment firm managing approximately $2.6 billion in regulatory assets under management, released a presentation to the Independent Directors of KeyCorp entitled "Read My Lips: No New Acquisitions."

headline: KeyCorp (KEY): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: KeyCorp trades at $19.06 and has moved in lockstep with the market. Its shares have returned 19.8% over the last six months while the S&P 500 has gained 15.3%.
